extends website.pug

block header
  title Steemfounders

append scripts
    script(src='/js/main.js')

block body
  body
    include partials/navbar.pug

    .hero-area
      .particleground
      .hero-items
        .container
          .row
            .col-md-6.col-sm-10.col-xs-12
              h2 Steem needs valuable users. Steem needs you!
              p
                | We want to make it easier for new and valuable creators to quickly create their accounts so that they can share their content with us and monetize it. Here we will let you publish your first post to fund new account as soon as possible.
              ul
                li
                  a(href='#introduce') Introduce Yourself
                li
                  a(href='https://signup.steemit.com/')
                    | Or use Steemit
                    i.fa.fa-long-arrow-right
            .col-md-6.text-right.hidden-sm.hidden-xs
              img(src='/images/steemfounders.png', alt='')

    .pricing-table-area
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1.col-xs-12
            .section-title.text-center
              h2 How it works
              p
                | Steemfounders allows you to publish your first post here without having an account. Try to make it as good as possible - at Steemit we reward interesting creators and it will depend on how quickly your account will be created (however, it should not take longer than 24 hours).
        .row
          .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
            .service-wrap.text-center
              h3 You introduce yourself
              img(src='/images/service/1.png', alt='')
              p
                | All you have to do is write your first post here - if it is good enough, your account will be opened even today. Remember - this post should be your trademark, try to be as good as possible
          .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
            .service-wrap.text-center
              h3 We fund your new account
              img(src='/images/service/2.png', alt='')
              p
                | If your post looks good, we take the risk and finance a new account especially for you. You will receive all the access keys to this account. This will be 
                strong YOUR
                |  account, ready to publish your next materials immediately.
              // <a href="single-service.html">Read more</a>
          .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
            .service-wrap.text-center
              h3 You receive all rewards
              img(src='/images/service/3.png', alt='')
              p
                | We want to be fair with our users, so after 7 days, when your work will be settled, we transfer the tokens earned by you to your wallet. It will be yours and you will be able to withdraw them or invest in account power
              // <a href="single-service.html">Read more</a>
    // service-area end
    // quote-area start
    .quote-area
      .particleground
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-7
            .quote-wrap
              p
                | Every successful individual knows that his or her achievement depends on a community of persons working together.
    // quote-area end
    // fanfact-area start
    .fanfact-area.pricing-table-area
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-12
            .fanfact-wrap
              h2.counter= account_number
              p Accounts funded
          .col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-12
            .fanfact-wrap
              h2.counter= steem_transfered
              p STEEM tokens transfered
          .col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-12
            .fanfact-wrap
              h2.counter= sbd_transfered
              p SBD tokens transfered
    // fanfact-area end
    // expert-area start
    .expert-area
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1.col-xs-12
            .section-title.text-center
              h2 Latest posts
        .row
          each post in latest
            .col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              .blog-wrap
                .blog-img
                  img(src=post.image, alt='')
                .blog-content
                  h3= post.title
                  a(href='https://steemit.com/@steemfounders/' + post.permlink) Read on Steemit

    #introduce.pricing-table-area
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1.col-xs-12
            .section-title.text-center
              h2 Introduce yourself
              p
                | First of all you need to authenticate your account. Just type your email into form below. Don't worry, we hate spam too, so we will use your e-mail only for sending information about accepting your post and creating account. It won't be shared with anyone. Never.

              p If you cant see registration form below, please try disabling your ad-blocking extensions.
        .row
          .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-2.col-xs-12
            .newsletter-wrap
              form#register
                input#new-mail(type='email', placeholder='Your email here', name='email')
                button(type='submit', name='button') Send activation link
    
    block footer
      include partials/footer.pug